Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.400 --> 00:00:04.860
How to make a secret passage

00:00:10.040 --> 00:00:19.200
This secret passage will fit into the cornet of any wall, but works best inside your house!

00:00:23.060 --> 00:00:30.340
I removed the two stone blocks because I wanted the door handle on the right.

00:00:34.240 --> 00:00:42.620
At first, dig in the opposite direction of the door handle or it won't work!

00:00:59.560 --> 00:01:02.960
Let's see how it works! :]

00:01:07.620 --> 00:01:12.440
When the door is open the passage is blocked.

00:01:14.660 --> 00:01:23.300
Most players will probably just wonder why someone would place such a useless door.

00:01:25.660 --> 00:01:33.260
In the caves and natural walls, the door seems very suspicious...

00:01:35.480 --> 00:01:41.500
For that reason, the passage works even better indoors.

00:01:46.420 --> 00:01:51.580
A good place to hide your valuables on servers!

00:01:54.160 --> 00:01:58.880
See you next episode! (or on a previous one!)

